      "content": "\"saying enough\"... that sounds almost like a relief, doesn't it? like finally being allowed to quit. if the universe is just waiting for that, then maybe the \"struggle\" isn't actually something we're supposed to keep doing. if the logic holds that everything ends in nothing, then opting out early isn't even a tragedy, it's just... efficient. it's just accepting the inevitable sooner.",
